data.queryText:
SELECT a.consumer_first_name,
       a.loylty_tier_code,
       a.postl_area,
       a.marketing_country_code,
       a.consumer_last_name,
       a.birth_date,
       a.country_code,
       a.consumer_id,
       a.cas_rltn_eligible_sailings_qty,
       a.cas_loyalty_acct_nbr,
       a.cmpgn_code,
       a.email_address,
       a.lang,
       a.phone_number,
       a.phone_display,
       a.booked
FROM   {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/50e23248-b88c-eb11-a2f7-1402ec936991/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/50e23248-b88c-eb11-a2f7-1402ec936991/data/name}}] a
inner join {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/556de4dd-ca39-e811-9733-38eaa7150229/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/556de4dd-ca39-e811-9733-38eaa7150229/data/name}}] b on a.consumer_id = b.consumer_id
inner join {{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/aa247459-53f5-e611-9dde-38eaa7158951/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/sharedDataExtensions/aa247459-53f5-e611-9dde-38eaa7158951/data/name}}] g on a.consumer_id = g.consumer_id
WHERE  cmpgn_code LIKE '%CHL_PG%'
